Microwave ablation vs. surgery for papillary thyroid carcinoma with minimal 
sonographic extrathyroid extension: a multicentre prospective study.

Zheng L(#)(1), Dou JP(#)(1), Liu FY(1), Yu J(1), Cheng ZG(1), Yu XL(1), Wang 
H(2), Liu C(3), Yu MA(4), Cong ZB(5), Wang SR(6), Che Y(7), Xu ZF(8), Hao Y(9), 
Bai N(10), Wang X(5), Liu Y(6), Zhou Y(8), Shi J(11), Fu ZH(12), Zhan HY(13), 
Han ZY(14), Liang P(15).

Author information:
(1)Department of Interventional Ultrasound, Chinese PLA General Hospital, No.28 
Fuxing Road, Haidian District, Beijing, 100853, China.
(2)Department of Ultrasound, China-Japan Union Hospital of Jilin University, No. 
