Does the Structure Matter? An External Validation and Health Economic Results 
Comparison of Event Simulation Approaches in Severe Obesity.

Schwander B(1)(2), Kaier K(3), Hiligsmann M(4), Evers S(4)(5), Nuijten M(6).
